  # Wasted 10 years with Bash
  
  ## Try Fish or ZSH — modern Bash alternatives that make shell more productive and cool. Do not waste time with Bash as I did.
  
  [![Adam Brodziak](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*HdV-_9ULgFzVS0x4IJzyOA.jpeg)](https://adambrodziak.medium.com/?source=post_page---byline--a7f6cb480419---------------------------------------)
  
